Édition de 1899</td>
<td width="33%" style="text-align:right;font-size:90%;"><a href="/wiki/Bible_du_Rabbinat_1899/Isa%C3%AFe" title="Bible du Rabbinat 1899/Isaïe">Isaïe</a><span class="%5B%5BBible+du+Rabbinat+1899%2FIsa%C3%AFe%7CIsa%C3%AFe%5D%5DhiddenStructure" style="color:#808080">&#160;&#160;►</span></td>
